shadow></value><value name=\"ADD7\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">Security cams have backup systems,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD8\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">so if you shut the power off,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD9\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">they will turn back on in 9 seconds.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD10\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">After that,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD11\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">It's impossible to shut it off.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD12\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">Steve has his radio broken,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD13\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">so we can't communicate the timing.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD14\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">Thankfully he only needs 7 seconds.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD15\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">To get the money, and to get out.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD16\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">So, when you hear him coming,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD17\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">make sure to turn off the cams.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD18\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">Don't do it immediately, though.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD19\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">If you do, the cams will come back,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD20\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">catching Steve in the act.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD21\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">Don't let us down.</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD22\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">And make sure not to confuse noises,</field></shadow></value><value name=\"ADD23\"><shadow type=\"text\"><field name=\"TEXT\">not e